--- teams [feature] ---
TeamsCont  [C]    : Team management routes | $auth → THIS → TeamsSer
TeamsSer   [S]    : Team management business logic | TeamsCont ← THIS → TeamsRepo ⇒ EvtTeamsChanged
TeamsRepo  [R]    : teams tables, RLS $tenant | TeamsSer ← THIS → $db
TeamsType  [T]    : Teams, CreateTeamsDto, UpdateTeamsDto
TeamsVal   [V]    : Zod schemas for teams input | TeamsCont ← THIS
TeamsTest  [X]    : unit + integration tests
